## Neo4j Naming Ontology

Reference: https://neo4j.design/40a8cff71/p/5993ea-naming-ontology

### Product Names

| Correct | Incorrect |
|---------|-----------|
| Neo4j Aura | Aura, Neo4j aura, AURA |
| Neo4j Desktop | Desktop, Neo4j desktop |
| Neo4j Browser | Browser, Neo4j browser |
| Neo4j Bloom | Bloom, Neo4j bloom |
| GraphAcademy | Graph Academy, graphacademy |

