### Technical Terms

| Term | Definition | Usage |
|------|------------|-------|
| **Instance** | A running Neo4j database in Aura | "Create an instance" |
| **Database** | The data store within an instance | "Query the database" |
| **Node** | A graph data entity | "Person nodes" |
| **Relationship** | A connection between nodes | "ACTED_IN relationship" |
| **Property** | Key-value data on nodes/relationships | "name property" |
| **Label** | Category tag on nodes | "Movie label" |
| **Cypher** | Neo4j query language | Always capitalized |

